<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>عَبْد ُ الرَّزَّاقِ،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١١٣٢٥ - عَنِ الثَّوْرِيِّ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ عَبْدِ الرَّحْمَنِ ابن الْأَصْبَهَانِيِّ قَالَ:</span> قَالَ عِكْرِمَةُ: <span class="c2">«الْحِينُ سِتَّةُ أَشْهُرٍ»</span>.<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ ابْنُ الْمُسَيِّبِ:</span> <span class="c2">«أَسْفَرَهَا عِكْرِمَةُ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>